{
  "stem": "8784.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And so our-- our living there-- during the time that we were there, some stray railroad cars would arrive in there, and frozen people would be found in the railroad cars.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Mr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Schindler had a great deal to do with that by-- by helping, her physically helping the inmates to unload those people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Some of them in the railroad cars were frozen, were dead, were horribly injured.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Some of the skin-- on some of those that were still alive, some of the skin was froze to the wooden floors or walls of the railroad cars.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "This was winter time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But some of them remained alive and were brought back to health in our camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did-- on some occasion, I did participate if I wasn't away, if I was in the camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody had a hand in going out to help with the unloading.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And rumor would have it at that time that Schindler was not producing anything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And not only was this a rumor, but from my own experience, I also knew it, that we are not producing anything.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We are not making anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We're building offices.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We are making cabinets.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We are maintaining blackout shades.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We are doing many things, but there is no productivity as such.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was inside this great factory hall, there was a surrounded area by wire.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was separated from the rest of the hall from where I work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And inside that wired-off area were the people that were working on the lathe and producing some samples and producing some machinery, preparing machinery like if the war was going to last forever.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they were planning and scheming some new equipment, new machinery, and working on that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And this was on the inside of the big hall.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
